How to prevent more than one call because it's getting called too many times

To prevent the fetchData function from being called too many times, you can add a memoization technique to cache the results of the API call. Here's an example of how to implement it with a simple JavaScript object used as a cache:

```javascript
const CACHE = {};

export async function fetchData(indicator, countryCode) {
  const { endpoint } = apiUrlsAndIndicators.find(i => i.indicator === indicator);
  const cacheKey = `${countryCode}_${endpoint}`;

  // If the data is cached, return it directly
  if (CACHE[cacheKey]) {
    return CACHE[cacheKey];
  }

  const url = `${BASE_URL}${countryCode}/indicator/${endpoint}?format=json`;

  try {
    const response = await fetch(url);
    const data = await response.json();
    console.log(data);
    let indicatorData = data[1][0];
    let i = 0;
    while (indicatorData.value === null && i < data[1].length) {
      i++;
      indicatorData = data[1][i];
    }
    if (indicatorData === null) {
      return indicatorData;
      throw new Error('All values in data array are null');
    }

    // Cache the result before returning it
    CACHE[cacheKey] = indicatorData;
    return indicatorData;
  } catch (error) {
    /* console.error(error); */
    return null;
  }
}
```

By using the `CACHE` object, the function will store the results of the API calls and return them directly instead of making a new API call when the function is called with the same `indicator` and `countryCode` as before.

Keep in mind that the cache will persist only as long as the script is running. If you need a more advanced or long-term caching mechanism, you can consider using something like IndexedDB or the Cache API in the browser.

在 Spring Boot 应用程序中，可以使用过滤器（filter）来过滤和清理 HTML 标签和其他未受信任的内容，以防止 XSS 攻击。

以下是在 Spring Boot 应用程序中使用过滤器来过滤 XSS 的示例：

1. 创建一个 XSS 过滤器类，实现 Servlet Filter 接口，并实现其 doFilter 方法：

```
import javax.servlet.*;
import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;
import java.io.IOException;

public class XssFilter implements Filter {

    @Override
    public void init(FilterConfig filterConfig) throws ServletException {

    }

    @Override
    public void doFilter(ServletRequest request, ServletResponse response, FilterChain chain) throws IOException, ServletException {
        HttpServletRequest req = (HttpServletRequest) request;
        HttpServletResponse resp = (HttpServletResponse) response;

        chain.doFilter(new XssRequestWrapper(req), resp);
    }

    @Override
    public void destroy() {

    }
}
```

2. 创建一个 XSS 请求包装类 XssRequestWrapper，该类继承 HttpServletRequestWrapper，并覆盖需要筛选的方法，如 getParameter、getHeader、getParameterMap、getHeaderMap 和 getCookies：

```
import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequestWrapper;
import java.util.*;

public class XssRequestWrapper extends HttpServletRequestWrapper {

    public XssRequestWrapper(HttpServletRequest request) {
        super(request);
    }

    @Override
    public String getParameter(String name) {
        String value = super.getParameter(name);
        if (value != null) {
            value = cleanXss(value);
        }
        return value;
    }

    @Override
    public Map<String, String[]> getParameterMap() {
        Map<String, String[]> parameterMap = super.getParameterMap();
        Iterator<Map.Entry<String, String[]>> iterator = parameterMap.entrySet().iterator();
        while (iterator.hasNext()) {
            Map.Entry<String, String[]> entry = iterator.next();
            String[] values = entry.getValue();
            for (int i = 0; i < values.length; i++) {
                values[i] = cleanXss(values[i]);
            }
            parameterMap.put(entry.getKey(), values);
        }
        return parameterMap;
    }

    @Override
    public Enumeration<String> getParameterNames() {
        return Collections.enumeration(getParameterMap().keySet());
    }

    @Override
    public String[] getParameterValues(String name) {
        String[] values = super.getParameterValues(name);
        if (values != null) {
            for (int i = 0; i < values.length; i++) {
                values[i] = cleanXss(values[i]);
            }
        }
        return values;
    }

    @Override
    public String getHeader(String name) {
        String value = super.getHeader(name);
        if (value != null) {
            value = cleanXss(value);
        }
        return value;
    }

    @Override
    public Map<String, String> getHeaderMap() {
        Map<String, String> headerMap = new HashMap<>();
        Enumeration<String> headerNames = super.getHeaderNames();
        while (headerNames.hasMoreElements()) {
            String headerName = headerNames.nextElement();
            headerMap.put(headerName, getHeader(headerName));
        }
        return headerMap;
    }

    @Override
    public Enumeration<String> getHeaderNames() {
        return super.getHeaderNames();
    }

    @Override
    public Enumeration<String> getHeaders(String name) {
        return super.getHeaders(name);
    }

    @Override
    public Cookie[] getCookies() {
        Cookie[] cookies = super.getCookies();
        if (cookies != null) {
            for (Cookie cookie : cookies) {
                cookie.setValue(cleanXss(cookie.getValue()));
            }
        }
        return cookies;
    }

    private String cleanXss(String value) {
        // TODO: 过滤 HTML 标签和其他不受信任的内容，如 JavaScript、CSS 等
        return value;
    }
}
```

3. 在 Spring Boot 应用程序中注册过滤器：

```
@Configuration
public class WebConfig {

    @Bean
    public FilterRegistrationBean<XssFilter> xssFilterRegistrationBean() {
        FilterRegistrationBean<XssFilter> registrationBean = new FilterRegistrationBean<>();
        registrationBean.setFilter(new XssFilter());
        registrationBean.addUrlPatterns("/*");
        registrationBean.setName("xssFilter");
        registrationBean.setOrder(1); // 执行顺序
        return registrationBean;
    }
}
```

在 cleanXss 方法中，需要编写代码来过滤 HTML 标签和其他未受信任的内容，例如使用 HtmlUtils.htmlEscape 方法来转义 HTML 和 JavaScript 标签。

