      }
    ]
  },
  ...
]
```

The response will include an array of objects representing each product on your store, with fields such as `id`, `title`, `body_html`, `vendor`, `product_type`, `variants`, `images`, etc. You can filter and sort the list by adding query parameters to the endpoint URL.

